<view>
  <swiper indicator-dots="{{true}}" autoplay="{{true}}">
    <swiper-item>
      <image src="/images/wx.png"></image>
    </swiper-item>
    <swiper-item>
      <image src="/images/iqiyi.png"></image>
    </swiper-item>
    <swiper-item>
      <image src="/images/vr.png"></image>
    </swiper-item>
  </swiper>
  <!-- wx:if 判断 -->
  <!-- wx:for 循环 xw:for-item 子元素值，默认为item xw:index 序号，默认index -->
  <block wx:for="{{data1}}">
    <!-- <text>{{index}}</text> -->
    <view class="post-containet">
      <view class="post-author-date">
        <image class="post-author" src="{{item.img}}"></image>
        <text class="post-date">{{item.date}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="post-title">{{item.message.title}}</text>
      <image class="post-image" src="/images/post/crab.png"></image>
      <text class="post-content">菊黄蟹正肥，品尝秋之味。徐志摩把,“看初花的荻芦”和“到楼外楼吃蟹”,并列为秋天来杭州不能错过的风雅之事；用林妹妹的话讲是“螯封嫩玉双双满，</text>
      <view class="post-like"> 
        <image class="post-like-image" src="../../images/icon/chat.png"></image>
        <text class="post-like-font">96</text>
        <image class="post-like-image" src="/images/icon/view.png"></image>
        <text class="post-like-font">112</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
